{"tid":1456241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場手足快啲走呀！","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:19:49.000Z","uid":172701,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3abc2b2309f89b35c9c4a8c5be66cce2d233a9a9","tid":1456241,"uid":172701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:53:18.000Z","msg":"周圍都好多鬼係咁叫人唔好走<br />\n千奇唔好送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目標已經達成<br />\n如果無左旅客已經無意義<br />\n萬一交通封鎖就困獸鬥<br />\n<br />\n快啲離開"},{"pid":"411fd520edb513784acb8aeaba1761523b350ac1","tid":1456241,"uid":93940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"已經成功癱瘓機場喇。<br />\n仲要打持久戰㗎！快啲走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434ac9185cc182975ff4f29a049a323b38409272","tid":1456241,"uid":113784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:53:47.000Z","msg":"1. 我哋目的係向外宣傳，冇機冇旅客，等於冇宣傳<br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋目的可能係癱瘓機場，依家所有班機都取消，已經癱瘓咗機場<br />\n<br />\n留低有咩做？？自己問下自己。<br />\n<br />\n到時機場回復運作咪再入過囉，更加唔好講夜晚收工接力的手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b48efc4704270938e83da82b52e5bc4d5d9fe7","tid":1456241,"uid":200957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:53:51.000Z","msg":"快走呀  機鐵已停喇"},{"pid":"18f7855353ceebd5c546f6665a606e3e88f6599b","tid":1456241,"uid":200957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:10.000Z","msg":"有巴士都開始唔停T1  困獸鬥架"},{"pid":"1f00d78754b3551cd8477bfcb01d26259323e16b","tid":1456241,"uid":172701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:24.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n手足勿送頭<br />\n少你一個就少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36adadf7e9877fa490c02bb9bbb54b3cc9f352a3","tid":1456241,"uid":114632,"lik